getAllowedTemplates

public Set<PageObject> getAllowedTemplates(UUID pageId)
                                    throws PMSException
Returns the set of templates allowed to be used by a page. If the page is a template itself, it is not included in the returned collection.

Parameters:
pageId - Page Id.
Returns:
The set of allowed templates. If the argument is null or it is not found in the portal all templates are returned.
Throws:
PMSException
